{{vgname2|Blendo Games}}是一家位于[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[卡尔弗城_(加利福尼亚州)|卡尔弗城]]的{{tsl|en|Indie game development|独立游戏开发|独立}}[[电子游戏|电子游戏]]开发公司。公司最初由布兰登·钟（Brendon Chung）一人于2010年成立。Blendo Games凭借简约的独立游戏《[[严肃的骨头|严肃的骨头]]》获得了广泛曝光，其不久后开发的《[[星系舰队|星系舰队]]》和《{{tsl|en|Atom Zombie Smasher||原子僵尸粉碎机}}》也受到了好评。工作室还发布了多种类型的游戏。

==背景==
[[File:Brendon_chung_cropped.jpg|thumb]]]]

钟在被聘为[[Pandemic_Studios|Pandemic Studios]]的设计师之前，做了大约10年的业余编程工作，比如《[[雷神之锤II|雷神之锤II]]》和《[[半条命_(游戏)|半条命]]》等游戏的[[游戏模组|修改]]<ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/292143/Road_to_the_IGF_Blendo_Games_Quadrilateral_Cowboy.php|title=Road to the IGF: Blendo Games' Quadrilateral Cowboy|last=Wawro|first=Alex|website=www.gamasutra.com|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401230958/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/292143/Road_to_the_IGF_Blendo_Games_Quadrilateral_Cowboy.php|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="kotaku decade">{{cite web | url = https://kotaku.com/blendo-games-has-been-at-it-for-10-years-and-has-consi-1840794372 | title = Blendo Games Has Been At It For 10 Years, And Has Consistently Kicked Ass | first = Heather | last = Alexander | date = 2020-01-03 | accessdate = 2020-01-14 | work = [[Kotaku|Kotaku]] | archive-date = 2020-01-14 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200114164701/https://kotaku.com/blendo-games-has-been-at-it-for-10-years-and-has-consi-1840794372 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。当时他参与了《{{le|指环王：征服|The Lord of the Rings: Conquest}}》和《{{le|全能战士十锤|Full Spectrum Warrior: Ten Hammers}}》的研发，尽管他还在从事个人项目，包括一个剧情性的《公民亚伯》（''Citizen Abel''）系列以及传统[[第一人称射击游戏|第一人称射击游戏]]<ref name="kotaku decade"/>。钟认为他的首款正式发行游戏是2008年的间谍游戏《[[严肃的骨头|严肃的骨头]]》<ref name="kotaku decade"/><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.criticalpathproject.com/mind/brendon-chung/|title=Brendon Chung|website=insights from the greatest minds in video games.|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401231022/https://www.criticalpathproject.com/mind/brendon-chung/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/11/15/level-with-me-brendon-chung/|title=Level With Me, Brendon Chung.|date=|publisher=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|accessdate=2019-03-03|archive-date=2019-03-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190324130337/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2011/11/15/level-with-me-brendon-chung/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.offworld.com/2009/01/gimme-indie-game-gravity-bone.html |title=Archived copy |accessdate=2010-02-12 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090406045503/http://offworld.com/2009/01/gimme-indie-game-gravity-bone.html |archivedate=2009-04-06 }}</ref>。2009年11月，[[艺电|艺电]]关闭了Pandemic Studios，钟开始了太空战斗游戏《[[星系舰队|星系舰队]]》的开发，这是一款借鉴了他先前从事的一个废弃个人项目的太空战斗游戏。《星系舰队》于2010年正式发行<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-flotilla/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140316105857/http://www.edge-online.com/features/making-flotilla/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2014-03-16|title=The Making Of: Flotilla {{!}} Features {{!}} Edge Online|date=2014-03-16|access-date=2019-03-12}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.pcgamer.com/new-steam-games-august-19/|title=Five new Steam games you probably missed this week (August 19, 2018)|last=Macgregor|first=Jody|date=2018-08-20|website=PC Gamer|language=|access-date=2019-03-09|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401230955/https://www.pcgamer.com/new-steam-games-august-19/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

同年晚些时候，Blendo Games发布了《空中堡垒》（''Air Forte''），这是一款{{le|寓教于乐的游戏|Educational entertainment}}，玩家可以根据提示驾驶飞机来学习数学、地理和词汇知识<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blendogames.com/airforte/index.htm|title=AIR FORTE Official Site|website=blendogames.com|access-date=2019-03-11|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401230853/http://blendogames.com/airforte/index.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gameandplayer.net/articles/2010/07/air_forte.html|title=Air Forte on Game and Player|website=www.gameandplayer.net|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-09-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190913124216/http://www.gameandplayer.net/articles/2010/07/air_forte.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://bit-tech.net/reviews/gaming/pc/air-forte-review/1/|title=Air Forte Review {{!}} bit-tech.net|website=bit-tech.net|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401231047/https://bit-tech.net/reviews/gaming/pc/air-forte-review/1/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，钟发行了[[即时战略游戏|即时战略游戏]]《{{le|原子僵尸粉碎机|Atom Zombie Smasher}}》，并得到了广泛好评，游戏在2011年[[PAX游戏展|便士街机游戏博览会]]上亮相，同时也是第三届[[Humble_Indie_Bundles|Humble Indie Bundles]]慈善活动的一部分<ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39190/Gamasutra_Best_Of_2011_Top_5_PC_Games.php | title = Gamasutra Best Of 2011: Top 5 PC Games | first = Tom | last = Curtis | date =2011-12-19| accessdate = 2011-12-19 | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | archive-date = 2012-01-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120107205353/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/39190/Gamasutra_Best_Of_2011_Top_5_PC_Games.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = http://igf.com/2012/01/2012_independent_games_festiva_3.html | title = 2012 Independent Games Festival Announces Main Competition Finalists | date = 2012-01-10 | accessdate = 2012-01-10 | publisher = [[独立游戏节|Independent Games Festival]] | dead-url = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20120113003228/http://igf.com/2012/01/2012_independent_games_festiva_3.html | archivedate = 2012-01-13 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/07/pax-10-2011-indie-games/ | title = 10 Clever Indie Games Ready to Shine at PAX | first = Jason | last = Schrier | date = 2011-07-13 | accessdate = 2011-08-05 | work = [[连线|Wired]] | archive-date = 2011-07-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110729040722/http://www.wired.com/gamelife/2011/07/pax-10-2011-indie-games/ | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/69613/humble-indie-bundle-3-adds-atom-zombie-smasher | title = Humble Indie Bundle 3 adds 'Atom Zombie Smasher' | first = Xav | last = de Matos | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2011-08-05 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-date = 2012-09-24 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120924092912/http://www.shacknews.com/article/69613/humble-indie-bundle-3-adds-atom-zombie-smasher | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《严肃的骨头》的续作《三十航班之恋》是为了支持[[Kickstarter|Kickstarter]]的{{le|Idle Thumbs}}播客项目而开发，并于2012年发行<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/163142/Kickstarter_drive_offers_exclusive_game_from_Atom_Zombie_Smasher_dev.php | title = Kickstarter drive offers exclusive game from Atom Zombie Smasher dev   | publisher = [[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]] | date = 2012-02-28 | accessdate = 2012-02-28 | first = Eric | last = Caoili | archive-date = 2012-03-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120301235607/http://gamasutra.com/view/news/163142/Kickstarter_drive_offers_exclusive_game_from_Atom_Zombie_Smasher_dev.php | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>[http://www.blendogames.com/ Blendo Games] {{Wayback|url=http://www.blendogames.com/ |date=20200701044542 }}. Retrieved March 7, 2012.</ref><ref name="sequel1">Meer, Alec (February 28, 2012). [http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/02/28/gravity-bones-sequel-thirty-flights-of-loving/ "Gravity Bone’s Sequel: Thirty Flights Of Loving"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2012/02/28/gravity-bones-sequel-thirty-flights-of-loving/ |date=20200803095102 }}. Rock Paper Shotgun. Retrieved March 7, 2012.</ref>。在《三十航班之恋》后，钟开始了对《四边形牛仔》为期四年的开发工作，最终游戏于2016年发行<ref name=":2" /><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/04/29/quadrilateral-cowboy/|title=The curious case of 'Quadrilateral Cowboy'|website=Engadget|language=|access-date=2019-03-12|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402002629/https://www.engadget.com/2016/04/29/quadrilateral-cowboy/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.engadget.com/2016/07/11/quadrilateral-cowboy-release-date/|title=Become a 1980s hacker in 'Quadrilateral Cowboy' on July 25th|website=Engadget|language=|access-date=2019-03-09|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402002629/https://www.engadget.com/2016/07/11/quadrilateral-cowboy-release-date/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。《星系舰队2》是《星系舰队》的[[虚拟现实|虚拟现实]]型续作，于2018年8月发行<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2018/08/20/flotilla-2-released/|title=Flotilla 2 jacks in to blast off|last=O'Connor|first=Alice|date=2018-08-20|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|language=|access-date=2019-03-12|archive-date=2019-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190329082304/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2018/08/20/flotilla-2-released/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2018年10月，Blendo Games透露一款名为《皮深》（''Skin Deep''）的新游戏正在开发中，不过发行日期尚未公布<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2018/10/17/blendo-skin-deep-stealth-fps-announced/|title=Skin Deep is Die Hard in space from the creator of Quadrilateral Cowboy|last=Tarason|first=Dominic|date=2018-10-17|website=Rock, Paper, Shotgun|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190330013740/https://www.rockpapershotgun.com/2018/10/17/blendo-skin-deep-stealth-fps-announced/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.destructoid.com/blendo-s-sneaky-shooter-skin-deep-draws-from-die-hard-and-far-cry-2-527383.phtml|title=Blendo's sneaky shooter Skin Deep draws from Die Hard and Far Cry 2|website=Destructoid|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2020-12-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201213204118/https://www.destructoid.com/blendo-s-sneaky-shooter-skin-deep-draws-from-die-hard-and-far-cry-2-527383.phtml}}</ref>。

==文化==
Blendo Games至今仍是一个单人工作室，不过根据《[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]》2016年的一个专题报道，钟在一间叫做Glitch City的{{le|共享办公室|Office sharing}}工作了一段时间<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/277643/WorkStation_The_spaces_where_22_different_gamemakers_build_worlds.php|title=WorkStation: The spaces where 22 different game-makers build worlds|last=Parkin|first=Simon|website=www.gamasutra.com|language=|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2019-04-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190401230858/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/277643/WorkStation_The_spaces_where_22_different_gamemakers_build_worlds.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他还直接与几个人合作过一些项目：《[[三十航班之恋|三十航班之恋]]》的乐谱由{{le|克里斯·雷莫|Chris Remo}}（Chris Remo）创作，《{{le|四边形牛仔|Quadrilateral Cowboy}}》的设计则是钟和泰南·威尔士（Tynan Wales）的共同努力。《四边形牛仔》的[[麦金塔操作系统|Mac]]和[[Linux|Linux]]端口由亚伦·梅尔切（Aaron Melcher）完成，游戏封面由伊桑·李（Ethan Lee）移植到这些平台。钟还表示，他得到了朋友和家人的帮助<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://blendogames.com/qc/faq.htm|title=Quadrilateral Cowboy FAQ|website=blendogames.com|access-date=2019-03-05|archive-date=2016-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160827180133/http://blendogames.com/qc/faq.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==《咖啡师》==
《咖啡师》是布兰登·钟为[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]开发的四个第一人称游戏系列，所有游戏都涉及玩家角色的觉醒<ref name="BLENDO: Older Projects">{{cite web|url=http://blendogames.com/older.htm|title=BLENDO: Older Projects|date=|publisher=Blendogames.com|accessdate=2013-10-08|archive-date=2013-08-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130820012051/http://blendogames.com/older.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

首款游戏是对《[[毁灭战士II|毁灭战士II: 人间地狱]]》的[[游戏模组|修改]]。在采访中，钟说首款游戏的灵感来自《{{le|毁灭圣经|Development of Doom}}》和Bungie的《{{tsl|en|Marathon (video game)|马拉松}}》<ref name=":0" /><ref name="BLENDO: Older Projects" />。

钟说第二款游戏是他在大学期间开发的一项独立研究项目<ref name=":0" />。游戏以一个无名的宇宙飞船驾驶员为中心，以一个脱节的故事情节为特点。游戏包括一个会说话的头骨和一个身份不明的女人等角色。头骨上提到一个叫汉娜的人，但是当采访者暗示这个身份不明的女人是汉娜时，钟说“她不是汉娜。你从没见过汉娜。”<ref name=":0" /><ref name="BLENDO: Older Projects" />

第三款游戏是《[[毁灭战士3|毁灭战士3]]》的[[游戏模组|模组]]<ref name="BLENDO: Older Projects"/>。

第四款游戏是《[[半条命2|半条命2]]》的[[游戏模组|模组]]。表示，他开发这个游戏是为了在一个更大的项目中使用[[id_Tech_4引擎|id Tech 4引擎]]之前学习它的限制条件<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/219590/Quadrilateral_Cowboy_Good_oldfashioned_digital_bliss.php|title=Quadrilateral Cowboy : Good old-fashioned digital bliss|last=Alexander|first=Leigh|website=www.gamasutra.com|language=|access-date=2019-03-11|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402042744/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/219590/Quadrilateral_Cowboy_Good_oldfashioned_digital_bliss.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

